    <td colspan="2"><p><span>Dadu's Sugar-Free Badamees delivers the rich, nutty flavour of almonds with zero to negligible sucrose content, vetted by rigorous lab testing. <br><br>Sweetened with Stevia, a natural plant-based sweetener, these sweet munchies are ideal for managing blood sugar levels and guilt free indulgence. With fewer calories, they are a great option for those mindful of their diet too. </span></p>
<p><span>Crafted with 100% natural ingredients and free from artificial additives, our badamees offer a delicious and healthy treat that perfectly balances taste and health benefits.</span></p>
<h3 dir="ltr"><span style="color: rgb(137, 6, 12);">What other Sugar Free Sweets does Dadus offer?</span></h3>
<p dir="ltr"><span>Dadus offers a variety of sugar-free sweets, including Kaju Katli, Mysore Pak, Golden Coin, Anjeer Dry Fruit Delight, Badamees, and Khajoor Coin, all crafted for a guilt-free indulgence. </span></p>
<h3 dir="ltr"><span style="color: rgb(137, 6, 12);">Can people with Diabetes/Sugar eat Dadus sugar free badamees?</span></h3>
<p dir="ltr"><span>Absolutely. People with diabetes can enjoy all of Dadu’s sugar-free offerings as they are sweetened with Stevia, suitable for blood sugar management. However, it is advisable for those with Type-1 Diabetes to consult their GP before consumption.</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span>Visit Dadu’s near you for a free tasting and gourmet experience. </span><span><br></span><span>In Hyderabad, explore our sweets on Swiggy &amp; Zomato for instant delivery. </span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span>All Dadu's sweets are fresh, vegetarian, and free from preservatives or artificial colours.</span></p>
